title: My Path Is To Become A Developer
description:
Description :
        The grandson of pharmaceutical company N, the perfect Alpha, 'Lee Tae-seong'.He was trying to get rid of his chaotic life and live quietly due to the management dispute, but his plans go awry when he meets Beta Ji Yu-bin'."I told you I was making games... I think I could develop other things too. Do you want to invest just once?"What should you do with a kid who wants to eat an Alpha?Beta Top (Ji Yu-bin) x Alpha Bottom (Lee Tae-seong)TL - HappyBunny
